#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:11
msgid "Support JIT Compilation in FFA"
msgstr "FFA 中的 JIT 编译支持"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:13
msgid ""
"In the development of large-scale deep learning frameworks and high-"
"performance kernel libraries, developers face a long-standing challenge: "
"balancing the support for **diverse kernel input configurations** (such as "
"data types, head dimensions, sparse/dense characteristics) against **the "
"exponential explosion of compilation time and binary size**. Since operators"
" are usually written using C++ templates and CUDA, Ahead-of-Time (AOT) "
"compilation of all possible parameter combinations causes the resulting "
"library sizes to skyrocket and the build process to become painfully slow."
msgstr ""
"在大规模深度学习框架和高性能 kernel 库的开发中，开发者面临一个长期挑战：在支持**多样化的 kernel 输入配置**（如数据类型、head "
"维度、稀疏/稠密特性）与**编译时间和二进制体积的指数级膨胀**之间取得平衡。由于算子通常使用 C++ 模板和 CUDA 编写，Ahead-of-"
"Time (AOT) 编译所有可能的参数组合会导致库体积急剧膨胀，构建过程变得极其缓慢。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:15
msgid ""
"To elegantly resolve this, `Flexible Flash Attention` (`FFA`) in "
"`MagiAttention` adopts a sophisticated yet lightweight **Just-In-Time (JIT) "
"compilation architecture**. This approach ensures peak runtime performance "
"while significantly improving development and distribution efficiency. In "
"this blog post, we will tear down the source code of `MagiAttention` to "
"reveal the inner workings of our JIT design."
msgstr ""
"为了优雅地解决这个问题，`MagiAttention` 中的 `Flexible Flash Attention` (`FFA`) 采用了精巧而轻量的 "
"**Just-In-Time (JIT) 编译架构**。这种方法在确保极致运行时性能的同时，显著提升了开发和分发效率。在这篇博客文章中，我们将深入剖析 "
"`MagiAttention` 的源代码，揭示 JIT 设计的内部运作机制。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:17
msgid "Acknowledgment"
msgstr "致谢"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:20
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Before diving in, we would like to extend our profound gratitude and respect"
" to the `FlashInfer` {cite}`ye2025flashinfer_jit_compile` team. Our JIT "
"infrastructure and caching codebase share many design philosophies and "
"actual implementation derivations from FlashInfer. Standing on the shoulders"
" of giants makes `MagiAttention`'s JIT compilation possible!"
msgstr ""
"在深入探讨之前，我们要向 `FlashInfer` {cite}`ye2025flashinfer_jit_compile` "
"团队致以深深的感谢和敬意。我们的 JIT 基础设施和缓存代码库与 FlashInfer "
"有着许多共同的设计理念和实际实现方面的借鉴。站在巨人的肩膀上，`MagiAttention` 的 JIT 编译才成为可能！"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:24
msgid "Why Do We Need a Custom JIT Strategy"
msgstr "为什么我们需要自定义 JIT 策略"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:26
msgid ""
"Let's look at the complex parameter space `MagiAttention` faces. `FFA` "
"provides a massive number of specialized options that need specific "
"optimization tweaks:"
msgstr "让我们来看看 `MagiAttention` 面临的复杂参数空间。`FFA` 提供了大量需要特定优化调整的专用选项："

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:28
msgid "**Forward and Backward** (`fwd`, `bwd`) pass differentiation."
msgstr "**前向和反向传播**（`fwd`、`bwd`）的区分。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:29
msgid "**Compute and Output Data Types** (`float16`, `bfloat16`, `float32`)."
msgstr "**计算和输出数据类型**（`float16`、`bfloat16`、`float32`）。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:30
msgid ""
"**Block Tiling Strategies** (e.g., adaptable `kblock_m` and `kblock_n`)."
msgstr "**分块策略**（例如可适配的 `kblock_m` 和 `kblock_n`）。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:31
msgid ""
"**Fine-grained optimization controls** (Softcap restrictions, Atomic "
"Reduction toggles, Auto Range Merge heuristics, SwapAB layouts, Group Query "
"Attention packs, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"**细粒度优化控制**（Softcap 限制、Atomic Reduction 开关、Auto Range Merge 启发式策略、SwapAB "
"布局、Group Query Attention 打包等）。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:33
msgid ""
"Exhausting all these combinations purely through AOT compilation would "
"produce an unwieldy binary size. Therefore, MagiAttention adopted a hybrid "
"strategy: **\"Selectively precompile (AOT) standard configurations, and "
"lazily load (JIT) rare combinations via dynamic generation.\"**"
msgstr ""
"纯粹通过 AOT 编译穷举所有这些组合将产生难以管理的二进制体积。因此，MagiAttention 采用了混合策略：**“选择性地预编译 (AOT) "
"标准配置，并通过动态生成惰性加载 (JIT) 罕见组合。”**"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:36
msgid "Deconstructing the Native Implementation"
msgstr "解构原生实现"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:38
msgid ""
"The core of MagiAttention's JIT framework resides in "
"`magi_attention/common/jit` and "
"`magi_attention/functional/_flex_flash_attn_jit.py`."
msgstr ""
"MagiAttention JIT 框架的核心位于 `magi_attention/common/jit` 和 "
"`magi_attention/functional/_flex_flash_attn_jit.py`。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:40
msgid "And the JIT pipeline consists of four major stages as follows:"
msgstr "JIT 流水线由以下四个主要阶段组成："

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:42
msgid "1. Signature Generation and Unique Identifiers (URI)"
msgstr "1. 签名生成与唯一标识符 (URI)"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:44
msgid ""
"When a Python operator (like `flex_flash_attn`) is invoked, the system first"
" inspects the user-provided parameters to generate a unique string-based "
"signature called the `URI`."
msgstr ""
"当 Python 算子（如 `flex_flash_attn`）被调用时，系统首先检查用户提供的参数，生成一个基于字符串的唯一签名，称为 `URI`。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:46
msgid ""
"In `_flex_flash_attn_jit.py`, the `get_ffa_uri` function structures this "
"label:"
msgstr "在 `_flex_flash_attn_jit.py` 中，`get_ffa_uri` 函数构造此标签："

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:60
msgid ""
"This URI essentially acts as an exact fingerprint for the compilation setup,"
" making it the perfect key for caching `.so` compilation outputs in local "
"disks and LruCaches."
msgstr "这个 URI 本质上是编译配置的精确指纹，使其成为在本地磁盘和 LruCache 中缓存 `.so` 编译输出的完美键值。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:62
msgid "2. Jinja2-Driven Code Template Rendering"
msgstr "2. Jinja2 驱动的代码模板渲染"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:64
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Unlike PyTorch's native JIT or custom C++ dispatcher methodologies that rely"
" on complex cascading macros, MagiAttention leverages the popular `Jinja2` "
"{cite}`jinja-api-documentation` templating engine to render purely specific "
"`.cu` instantiation scripts."
msgstr ""
"与 PyTorch 原生 JIT 或依赖复杂级联宏的自定义 C++ dispatcher 方法不同，MagiAttention 利用流行的 "
"`Jinja2` {cite}`jinja-api-documentation` 模板引擎来渲染纯粹特定的 `.cu` 实例化脚本。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:66
msgid ""
"At execution time, templates like `fwd_inst_template.jinja` are parsed:"
msgstr "在执行时，类似 `fwd_inst_template.jinja` 的模板会被解析："

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:80
msgid ""
"This dumps out an incredibly clean and minimal `.cu` file, totally isolated "
"from exhaustive `if constexpr` structures. Without those nested headers, "
"`NVCC` can parse and compile this rendered fragment blazing fast."
msgstr ""
"这会生成一个极其简洁的 `.cu` 文件，完全隔离于穷举式的 `if constexpr` 结构。没有那些嵌套头文件，`NVCC` "
"可以极速解析和编译这个渲染的片段。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:82
msgid "3. Ninja Concurrent Compilation and Locking (JitSpec)"
msgstr "3. Ninja 并发编译与锁机制 (JitSpec)"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:84
msgid ""
"With the source file now generated in "
"`.cache/magi_attention/generated/<URI>`, the JIT hands it over to our "
"`JitSpec` orchestrator. The pipeline is designed specifically for "
"performance kernels:"
msgstr ""
"源文件生成在 `.cache/magi_attention/generated/<URI>` 后，JIT 将其交给 `JitSpec` "
"编排器。该流水线专门为高性能 kernel 设计："

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:86
msgid ""
"**Generating `build.ninja`**: It prepares Ninja build manifests containing "
"aggressive CUTLASS and performance flags (`-O3`, `-use_fast_math`, "
"`-DCUTLASS_ENABLE_GDC_FOR_SM90`, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"**生成 `build.ninja`**：准备包含激进的 CUTLASS "
"和性能标志（`-O3`、`-use_fast_math`、`-DCUTLASS_ENABLE_GDC_FOR_SM90` 等）的 Ninja 构建清单。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:87
msgid ""
"**Locking and Multiprocessing Cache**: Real-world training scales out to "
"multiple GPUs and processes immediately. `FileLock` handles multi-process "
"safety preventing identical URI compilations from stepping on top of each "
"other."
msgstr "**锁与多进程缓存**：实际训练立即扩展到多个 GPU 和进程。`FileLock` 处理多进程安全性，防止相同 URI 的编译相互冲突。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:88
msgid ""
"**Dynamic Loading (.so)**: Once generated, `_import_module_from_library` "
"natively registers the dynamic library module to Python runtime."
msgstr ""
"**动态加载 (.so)**：生成后，`_import_module_from_library` 原生地将动态库模块注册到 Python 运行时。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:90
msgid "4. Seamless Synergy of JIT and AOT Processing"
msgstr "4. JIT 与 AOT 处理的无缝协同"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:92
msgid ""
"Nobody wants to watch their deep learning scripts freeze for 40 seconds on "
"epoch 1 because of a native compile, especially for standard parameters like"
" `head_dim=128`."
msgstr ""
"没有人希望自己的深度学习脚本在第 1 个 epoch 因原生编译而冻结 40 秒，尤其是对于 `head_dim=128` 这样的标准参数。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:94
msgid ""
"The most elegant feature of this architecture is that **AOT distribution "
"utilizes the exact same JIT engine script**."
msgstr "这个架构最优雅的特性是 **AOT 分发使用与 JIT 完全相同的引擎脚本**。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:96
msgid ""
"If you inspect `setup.py`, there is a neat parallel builder utilized during "
"project installation:"
msgstr "如果查看 `setup.py`，可以发现项目安装过程中使用了一个巧妙的并行构建器："

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:107
msgid ""
"The wheel packager loops through a combination list, leverages our "
"concurrent `ThreadPoolExecutor` and uses the JIT renderer to export the "
"`.so` plugins physically into the application directory."
msgstr ""
"wheel 打包器遍历组合列表，利用并发 `ThreadPoolExecutor`，使用 JIT 渲染器将 `.so` 插件实际导出到应用目录中。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:109
msgid "At runtime, the initial hook smoothly differentiates between the two:"
msgstr "在运行时，初始 hook 平滑地区分两者："

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:118
msgid ""
"This achieves a perfectly synergistic system: common setups are picked up "
"natively as AOT binaries from the packaged library, while exploratory "
"hyperparameter configs trigger a lightweight JIT compilation under the hood "
"logic smoothly."
msgstr ""
"这实现了一个完美协同的系统：常用配置从打包的库中作为 AOT 二进制文件被原生加载，而探索性的超参数配置则在底层逻辑中平滑地触发轻量级 JIT 编译。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:121
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "结论"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:123
msgid ""
"The architecture presented in MagiAttention brings a clean `Jinja2` and "
"`Ninja` driven deployment cycle layout:"
msgstr "MagiAttention 中呈现的架构带来了简洁的 `Jinja2` 和 `Ninja` 驱动的部署周期："

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:125
msgid ""
"**Developer Velocity**: No infinite recompiles triggered by altering a "
"generic core C++ template header."
msgstr "**开发效率**：修改通用核心 C++ 模板头文件不会触发无限次重新编译。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:126
msgid ""
"**Compact Distributions**: Eliminating bloated AOT switch-branches massively"
" cuts down output size."
msgstr "**紧凑分发**：消除臃肿的 AOT switch 分支，大幅缩减输出体积。"

#: ../../source/blog/jit_compile.md:127
msgid ""
"**Extreme Specializations**: Zero runtime penalty dynamically rendered "
"components tuned for the specific layer's demands."
msgstr "**极致特化**：零运行时开销的动态渲染组件，针对特定层的需求进行调优。"

